{"word":"G1744 - ἐνδύνω - endýnō - en-doo'-no - Creep","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐνδύνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">endýnō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en-doo'-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Creep</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நுழை"},{"paragraph":"1. to put on"},{"paragraph":"2. intransitive, to creep into, insinuate oneself into; to enter"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G1416 - δύνω - dýnō - doo'-no/1416\">G1416</a>; to <i>sink</i> (by implication <i>wrap</i> (compare <a href=\"#/G1746 - ἐνδύω - endýō - en-doo'-o/1746\">G1746</a>)) <i>on</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>sneak:</i> - creep.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1416/1416\">G1416</a>, <a href=\"#/G1562/1562\">G1562</a>, <a href=\"#/G1744/1744\">G1744</a>, <a href=\"#/G1902/1902\">G1902</a>, <a href=\"#/G554/554\">G554</a>, <a href=\"#/G555/555\">G555</a>"}]}